{% comment %}
  Homepage del portal B2B LedsC4 Outlet. Estética editorial sobria:
  dark hero + features + footer legal. Typography mix (serif display +
  sans body). Fully responsive, sin dependencias externas.

  Diseño estable (rethink 2026-04-19): contenido del hero NO depende del
  customer state. Mismo mensaje para anon, pendiente, rechazado y aprobado.
  La diferenciación vive en:
    - El header (sections/b2b-header-simple para no-aprobados; header-group
      Dawn para aprobados) — ver layout/theme.liquid.
    - Los CTAs del hero (cambian según login state para ahorrar clicks).
    - Los emails 01-06 (comunicación fuera de web).
    - Las páginas /pages/cuenta-* (safety net si acaban ahí).

  Esto simplifica la lógica y reduce bugs como el descubierto el 2026-04-19
  (customer sin tag se colaba al catálogo por falta de safety net).
{% endcomment %}

<section class="b2b-portal" aria-labelledby="b2b-portal-heading">

  <div class="b2b-portal__hero">
    <header class="b2b-portal__brand">
      {%- if shop.brand.logo != blank -%}
        <img
          src="{{ shop.brand.logo | image_url: width: 400 }}"
          alt="{{ shop.name | escape }}"
          width="180"
          height="auto"
          loading="eager"
        >
      {%- elsif section.settings.logo != blank -%}
        <img
          src="{{ section.settings.logo | image_url: width: 400 }}"
          alt="{{ shop.name | escape }}"
          width="{{ section.settings.logo_width | default: 180 }}"
          height="auto"
          loading="eager"
        >
      {%- else -%}
        <span class="b2b-portal__brand-wordmark">LEDS C4 <em>Outlet</em></span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </header>

    <div class="b2b-portal__hero-body">
      <p class="b2b-portal__eyebrow">Portal B2B · acceso exclusivo</p>
      <h1 id="b2b-portal-heading" class="b2b-portal__heading">
        Catálogo outlet
        <em>para profesionales</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="b2b-portal__lead">
        Stocks excedentes y descatalogados de LEDS C4 a precios reducidos.
        Acceso limitado a instaladores, arquitectos, distribuidores y retail del sector de la iluminación.
      </p>
      <div class="b2b-portal__ctas">
        {%- if customer and customer.tags contains 'aprobado' -%}
          <a href="/collections/coleccion-2026" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--primary">
            Ver catálogo
          </a>
          <a href="/account" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--secondary">
            Mi cuenta
          </a>
        {%- else -%}
          <a href="/account/login" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--primary">
            Iniciar sesión
          </a>
          <a href="/account/register" class="b2b-portal__btn b2b-portal__btn--secondary">
            Solicitar acceso
          </a>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="b2b-portal__scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
      <span>Más info</span>
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} Value prop features — solo visible si no es customer aprobado (a aprobado le interesa ver el catálogo directo). {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- unless customer.tags contains 'aprobado' -%}
    <div class="b2b-portal__features">
      <div class="b2b-portal__features-grid">
        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          <h3>Stock outlet</h3>
          <p>Excedentes, fin de serie y descatalogados de LEDS C4 a precios reducidos. Actualizado cada semana.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          <h3>Alta en 24-48h</h3>
          <p>Rellenas el formulario de solicitud y validamos tus datos profesionales. Sin mínimos en el primer pedido.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="b2b-portal__feature">
          <svg class="b2b-portal__feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
          <h3>Envío península 24-48h</h3>
          <p>Almacén ibérico con stock disponible. Envío directo y sin intermediarios para pedidos profesionales.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endunless -%}

  <footer class="b2b-portal__footer">
    <nav class="b2b-portal__footer-nav" aria-label="Enlaces legales">
      <a href="/pages/aviso-legal">Aviso legal</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href="/pages/politica-de-privacidad">Privacidad</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href="/pages/condiciones-de-uso">Condiciones</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href="/pages/canal-de-denuncias">Canal ético</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="b2b-portal__footer-note">
      © {{ 'now' | date: '%Y' }} LEDS C4, SA · CIF A59410910 · Carretera de Rubí 88, Sant Cugat del Vallés
    </p>
  </footer>

</section>

<style>
  .b2b-portal {
    --bg: #0c0e12;
    --bg-alt: #14171c;
    --fg: #f5f5f7;
    --fg-muted: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.68);
    --fg-dim: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.45);
    --accent: #d4a84a;
    --border: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.08);

    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--fg);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .b2b-portal *,
  .b2b-portal *::before,
  .b2b-portal *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .b2b-portal__hero {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 1px);
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(212, 168, 74, 0.08), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg-alt) 100%);
  }

  .b2b-portal__brand {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .b2b-portal__brand img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .b2b-portal__brand-wordmark {
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .b2b-portal__brand-wordmark em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  .b2b-portal__hero-body {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 680px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .b2b-portal__eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .b2b-portal__heading {
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .b2b-portal__heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 400;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .b2b-portal__heading em {
      display: inline;
    }
  }

  .b2b-portal__lead {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .b2b-portal__ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .b2b-portal__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 10.5rem;
    padding: 0.9375rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .b2b-portal__btn--primary {
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg);
  }
  .b2b-portal__btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .b2b-portal__btn--secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--fg);
    border: 1px solid var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .b2b-portal__btn--secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--fg);
    background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.04);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .b2b-portal__scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.75rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: b2b-bounce 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes b2b-bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, 6px); }
  }

  /* FEATURES */
  .b2b-portal__features {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .b2b-portal__features-grid {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .b2b-portal__feature {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .b2b-portal__feature-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    stroke-width: 1.25;
  }

  .b2b-portal__feature h3 {
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0 0 0.625rem;
    color: var(--fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .b2b-portal__feature p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .b2b-portal__footer {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .b2b-portal__footer-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.625rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .b2b-portal__footer-nav a {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .b2b-portal__footer-nav a:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .b2b-portal__footer-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .b2b-portal__btn,
    .b2b-portal__scroll-hint {
      transition: none;
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "B2B Portal Home",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-b2b-portal",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Branding"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "logo",
      "label": "Logo (fallback)",
      "info": "Se usa si Online Store > Brand > Logo está vacío. Fondo transparente; blanco sobre hero oscuro."
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "logo_width",
      "label": "Ancho del logo (px)",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 320,
      "step": 10,
      "default": 180
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "B2B Portal Home"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
